description:
WHAT IS IT?


Grab every hair, every time! Expertly shape your brows with MCoBeauty's Everyday Precision Tweezers. A set of baby pink tweezers, created using premium quality stainless steel that is durable and easy to clean.

The angled, slant tip allows for painless plucking and easily removes even the most stubborn hairs firmly from the root.



WHAT IT DOES:


  • Ultra-fine slant tips provides precise results
  • Perfectly calculated tension for optimum control
  • Made from easily cleanable & rust-proof high quality metal
  • Suitable for use on the face and body



    • WHY YOU'LL LOVE IT:


      • Perfectly sized for your handbag, desk or home
      • Premium & professional quality tweezers
      • Slant tip provides expert precision
      • Target stubborn hairs
name: Mcobeauty Everyday Precision Tweezer Each
